title: Bobby’s Scary Injury + Bobby Apologizes To Walker Hayes + Amy's Got Bobby Stressed
itunes:title: Bobby’s Scary Injury + Bobby Apologizes To Walker Hayes + Amy's Got Bobby Stressed
description:
Bobby had to call his doctor yesterday after a scary bike injury. Walker Hayes joins us to talk about his new song “Trash My Heart” and Bobby gives him a formal apology. Plus, Amy got Bobby's girlfriend Caitlin into a new activity that’s made his life more difficult….she’s now doing face peels!
